# Interactive stuff for a toddler

## == What is this ==

Simple interactive demos using Box2D for physics simulation and SDL2 for media and events. Something for a toddler to play around with safely and hopefully be entertained for a while.


## == How to run ==

Requires libbox2d, libsdl2, libsdl2-ttf and libsdl2-image.

Compile example:
```
g++ -std=gnu++11 box.c -lSDL2 -lBox2D -lSDL2_ttf -lSDL2_image -o boxgame
```


Run example:
```
./boxgame
```

